Package: LazyMatrix
Type: Package
Title: Allows lazy-loading of matrices from files or packages
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Michael Cary <michael.cary.dev@gmail.com>
Maintainer: Michael Cary <michael.cary.dev@gmail.com>
Description: The package provides the LazyMatrix class that extends the
  matrix class in base R to allow lazy-loading of matrix data from files
  or packages.  A LazyMatrix object has a small footprint in local memory,
  and therefore facilitates the handling of many large matrices at once.
License: GPL (>= 2)
Encoding: UTF-8
